videos.description: Courtney Vandersloot starts off hot from behind the arc with two 3-pointers for the Sky.
videos.headline: Vandersloot nets pair of deep 3s during Sky's 9-2 run

videos.description: Candace Parker sets up Rehema Stephens with a pinpoint pass for a Sky bucket.
videos.headline: Parker dishes no-look dime to Stephens for easy lay-in

videos.description: Jasmine Thomas steals the ball at midcourt, then takes it in for a basket plus the foul.
videos.headline: Thomas picks Vandersloot's pocket then finishes and-1

videos.description: Kahleah Copper reacts after the Sun are whistled for a foul on her reverse lay-in.
videos.headline: Copper fires up the crowd after and-1 for Sky
